Package problem2

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Actor
    This class extends the MediaArtist class and represents an actor with given details--name, age, genre, awards received, and lists of movies, TV series and other multimedia work the actor is involved in.
    Artist
    This class represents a general artist with given details--name, age, genre, and list of awards.
    ArtistTest
    Test class for the Artist class.
    Dancer
    This class extends the MediaArtist class and represents a dancer with given details--name, age, genre, awards received, and lists of movies, TV series and other multimedia work the dancer is involved in.
    Filmmaker
    This class extends the MediaArtist class and represents a filmmaker with given details--name, age, genre, awards received, and lists of movies, TV series and other multimedia work the filmmaker is involved in.
    MediaArtist
    This class represents a media artist, which include actor, dancer, and filmmaker, with additional given details--lists of movies, series, and other multimedia work the artist was involved with.
    MediaArtistTest
    Test class for the MediaArtist class.
    Musician
    This class extends the Artist class and represents a musician with given details--name, age, genre, and awards received.
    Painter
    This class extends the Artist class and represents a painter with given details--name, age, genre, and awards received.
    Photographer
    This class extends the Artist class and represents a photographer with given details--name, age, genre, and awards received.
    Poet
    This class extends the Artist class and represents a poet with given details--name, age, genre, and awards received.
